name: html-iron-news-layout
title: HTML/CSS/Git Intro - Iron News Layout
description: One of the basic, foundational skills in being a professional web developer is the translation of a designer's mockup image into a webpage with HTML and CSS. One of the basic, foundational news portals for professional web developers is Hacker News, which is kind of like a Reddit for the startup/design/development community with a very... *minimalist* design ethic.
